{
  "texts": [
    "The RNN layer has a time length of 5 years since we considered a 5-year yield dependencies.",
    "The RNN layer has LSTM cells with 64 hidden units.",
    "After trying different network designs, we found this architecture to provide the best overall performance.",
    "All weights were initialized with the Xavier method (Glorot and Bengio, 2010).",
    "We used stochastic gradient decent (SGD) with mini-batch size of 25."
  ]
}